data.description: Open 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Ranch with possible 4th bedroom/living space in converted garage. French doors in the back of the home opens to 0.4 acres of country living 1 of 2 sheds in fenced yard has been converted to a chicken coop. Large family room with wood burning fireplace and built in cabinets opens to large kitchen with tons of counter and cabinet space. This Brick Ranch is Minutes to downtown Suffolk and all areas of Hampton Roads.  Expanded driveway along side of home allows for U turns and room for multiple cars.  Expansive front yard sets this home well of Whaleyville.  Call/Text to arrange for a private tour and additional information.
